   ]

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import coolbox\n",
    "from coolbox.api import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [

     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "coolbox.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "test_hic = \"../../../tests/test_data/dothic_chr9_4000000_6000000.hic\"\n",
    "test_interval = \"chr9:4000000-6000000\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x975.118 with 15 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "with Feature(depth_ratio=0.5, color=\"RdYlBu_r\"):\n",
    "    raw = DotHiC(test_hic) + Title(\"Not smooth\")\n",
    "    with Feature(norm='log', transform=False):\n",
    "        smo0 = DotHiC(test_hic, gaussian_sigma=0.5) + MinValue(1e-1) + Title(\"Smooth\\nsigma=0.5\")\n",
    "        smo1 = DotHiC(test_hic, gaussian_sigma=1) + MinValue(1e-1) + Title(\"Smooth\\nsigma=1.0\")\n",
    "\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + raw + smo0 + smo1\n",
    "frame.plot(test_interval)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### CLI code"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%bash\n",
    "\n",
    "test_hic=\"../../../tests/test_data/dothic_chr9_4000000_6000000.hic\"\n",
    "\n",
    "coolbox add XAxis - \\\n",
    "    start_with Color \"RdYlBu_r\" - \\\n",
    "    start_with Feature --depth_ratio=\"0.5\" - \\\n",
    "    add DotHiC $test_hic - add Title \"Not smooth\" - \\\n",
    "    add DotHiC $test_hic --gaussian_sigma \"0.5\" --min_value \"1e-1\" - \\\n",
    "    add Title 'Smooth sigma=0.5' - \\\n",
    "    add DotHiC $test_hic --gaussian_sigma \"1.0\" --min_value \"1e-1\" - \\\n",
    "    add Title 'Smooth sigma=1.0' - \\\n",
    "    end_with - \\\n",
    "    end_with - \\\n",
    "    goto \"chr9:4000000-6000000\" - \\\n",
    "    plot /tmp/test_coolbox_smooth.png"
   ]
  }
